                  <p align="left">Sarris, Jonathan D.   1999.  &ldquo;&lsquo; Shot for Being  Bushwhackers&rsquo;: Guerrilla War and Extralegal Violence in a North Georgia  Community, 1862-1865&rdquo; [Lumpkin Co.].  In <em>Guerrillas,  Unionists, and Violence on the Confederate Home Front</em>, ed. D. Sutherland,  31-44.  Fayetteville: University of  Arkansas Press.</p>
